          "instruction": "Apply lateral surface area formula for cube",
          "working": "LSA = 4 × side² = 4 × 9² = 4 × 81",
          "result": "= 324 cm²",
          "voice_text": "Lateral surface area of a cube is 4 times side squared. 4 times 81 equals 324."
