          "instruction": "Apply CSA formula",
          "working": "CSA = 2πrh = 2 × (22/7) × 7 × 10",
          "result": "= 2 × 22 × 10 = 440 cm²",
          "voice_text": "Curved surface area of cylinder is 2 pi r h. 2 times 22 times 10 equals 440."
        }
      ],
